statements: SELECT * FROM mood_behavior_data
SELECT therapist_id, patient_id, mood_score FROM mood_behavior_data
SELECT session_id, session_date, mood_score FROM mood_behavior_data WHERE mood_score > 5
SELECT therapist_id, behavior_description FROM mood_behavior_data WHERE therapist_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000'
SELECT session_date, behavior_description FROM mood_behavior_data ORDER BY session_date DESC LIMIT 3
SELECT session_id, therapist_id, patient_id, session_date, mood_score, behavior_description FROM mood_behavior_data WHERE mood_score > 5 ORDER BY session_date DESC;
SELECT therapist_id, patient_id, AVG(mood_score) AS average_mood_score FROM mood_behavior_data GROUP BY therapist_id, patient_id;
SELECT session_id, therapist_id, patient_id, session_date, mood_score, behavior_description FROM mood_behavior_data WHERE session_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-28' ORDER BY mood_score ASC;
SELECT therapist_id, COUNT(DISTINCT patient_id) AS unique_patients FROM mood_behavior_data GROUP BY therapist_id HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT patient_id) > 1;
SELECT therapist_id, AVG(mood_score) AS average_mood_score, COUNT(*) AS total_sessions FROM mood_behavior_data GROUP BY therapist_id ORDER BY total_sessions DESC;
